<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.211946>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A) Dorsal and B) ventral views of holotype (UCR 19893) of Bolitoglossa aureogularis in life. C) Paratype (UCR 19857) of B. aureogularis in life. D) Dorsal view of right hand and E) right foot of holotype. Photos A, B and C by E. Boza-Oviedo and Roney Samaniego, D and E by Adrián García-Rodríguez. The bar in hand and feet are 1 mm length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/211946/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

